(42, 12, 55, 18, 37, 17, 17, 'south wind', 'Connection of South Wind Imagery', 'Both passages emphasize the south wind''s role in weather patterns. Luke discusses the prediction of heat from the south wind, while Job reflects on the warmth provided by the same wind.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
